result.name: Sapporo Japanese Ramen House

reviews.text: Nice Japanese ramen and food, value for money, small family run restaurant with warm hospitality

Good ramen
Good taste
Portion slightly on the small side
Food is good. Service too. Not special but very effective. Good casual and quick meals.
Quaint and nondescript, the place is run by a Japanese couple, I think. The food is really good; authentic Japanese food. The service is great, the staff are very polite, friendly, and welcoming.

Lunch set is bargain of choice. The taste of noodles likes the Sapporo original. However, seats are very narrow and the air-conditioning is weak, holding my backpack to eat the noodles, got sweat afterwards.....

result.name: 札幌日本拉麵屋

reviews.text:
商品写真より実物の方が良いですw地味にキャベツがいっぱいついてくるのってありがたい。吉野家だと謎の野菜になるので。味はまあまあ。味噌汁はマズイ。インスタントを日本からそのまま持ってきて欲しい。ソースは、さらにやばい。多分みんなオーダーしないから参加して腐ってるのだろうか酸っぱい。
全体としては嫌いじゃない。(味噌汁とソースをうまく回避すればオッケー👌)
好多不同選擇！豬扒蛋飯，鷄蛋嫩滑，洋蔥很香，豬扒肥瘦均勻，不油膩。
碗飯好的適，有啲想再叫多碗
